<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="virtual-speedway">Virtual Speedway</h3>
<h4 id="the-game">The game</h4>
<p>This is a virtual speedway game that allows you to place real money bets on the result of virtual motobike races shown continuously 24/7. A Play for Fun version of the game is not available.</p>
<p>All players playing the game at the same time, see the same races and the same results, wherever they are. All race simulations are created through a combination of Artificial Intelligence and independent random number generators.</p>
<h4 id="motoarena-torun-and-races">Motoarena Torun and races</h4>
<p>Race events are shown continuously. A new race event will start as soon as the current one has finished. A race event lasts approximately 2 minute. Each race has a fixed number of 4 participants.</p>
