<h4 id="betting">Betting</h4>
<p>Betting is allowed up to 10 seconds prior to the race start. Betting options for future races of the current race days remain open.</p>
<p>The following race betting options are available:</p>
<ol>
<li><p><strong>Win</strong> – bet on the selected Motobikes to win the race. (e.g., Motobike No.1 finishes 1st)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Place</strong>(1-2) – Bet on the selected Motobike to finish 1st or 2nd position in a race. (e.g., Selection 1: Motobike No.1 finishes 1st or 2nd)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Even/Odd</strong> – bet on No. Even (2/4) or No.Odd (1/3) to finish 1st position in a race.</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Over/Under</strong> – bet on the winner is over or under No.2.5 (Selection Over: Motobike No.3 or No.4 finishes 1st; Selection Under: Motobike No.1 or No.2 finishes 1st).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Exacta</strong> – bet on the 2 motobikes finishing in 1st and 2nd positions, in the order predicted. Both predictions must be correct for the bet to win. (e.g., Selection 1, 2: Motobike No.1 finishes 1st, Motobike No.2 finishes 2nd)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Quinella</strong> – bet on the 2 motobikes you expect to finish 1st and 2nd in any order. Both predictions must be correct for the best to win. (e.g., Selection1&amp;2: Motobike No.1 and No.2 finish 1st and 2nd in any order)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="your-bets">Your bets</h4>
<p>As you make your bet selections by clicking on the odds relating to the bet you wish to place, the betslip will open. Once you have made all your selections, enter your stake in the betslip Stake field and click on Bet. Your bet will be placed.</p>
<p>Virtual Speedway Racing bets cannot be combined in the same betslip with bets placed on real sport events.</p>
<p>If your bet is successful, your winnings will automatically be credited to your account.</p>
<p>To see the list of your Virtual Speedway bets, please go to Virtuals page and click on &quot;MY BETS&quot; next to &quot;BETSLIP&quot;. You will find a list of all bets you have placed. Also you can find details in the &quot;Bets History&quot; in the bottom of &quot;MY BETS&quot;.</p>
